<br>
I have been using my water pet for a lot of taking latley since I have just gotten a staff of water I have no need for cept for focus, I have also been duoing with my cleric so he can get exp faster since they changed the exp penalty thing with pets, efficent for him since he has to celestial once every 3 mobs or so. But in any case.<br>
<br>
Eleites in GD = Giants = massive HP compared to a non-giant mob thats the same level. Don't think it was a mystery why the earth pet couldnt solo those things since everything that is attacking a earth pet can hit it almost 100% of the time. Try useing a air pet or water pet.<br>
<br>
Raptors in TD can be a little tuff, but I figure if a wizzy can quad them (and I know of one that does so it is possible and it does happen) then I can single pull them and solo them. Again, try using a water pet or air pet over the earth pet.<br>
<br>
Ice giants are old world, should be very easy to kill. ravashing drolvargs (the biggest ones) in DL have roughly 3.5k hp and my water pet solo's em (with DS!!) and lives with 60% or so if all went well. So those Ice giants cant have more than 10k hp. Throw a couple of nukes in there and you should be fine while the pet finishes the rest of the giant. After all they are ice and should melt with a little heat (wink wink). Shouldnt be that though fer ya, after all your 58 now and you made it this far.<br>
<br>
If you can find me a wizard or a druid that can quad 4 times in a row without medding, then I want to congratulate them for there massivley uber gear.<br>
<br>
As far as those silly little Wyverns go in CS? Since VI/SoE fixed the pet/exp penalty, us mages can acually solo those little peckers till our hearts desire... Thats if there are enough Wyverns to go around.<br>
<br>
&lt;Cast 51 earth pet, DS, BO3, burst of flame birdie, go pet go, get exp, reclaim pet, wash, repeat&gt; med while the pet is killing.<br>
<br>
I did this once while I was very fortunate to get all of CS to myself with Volcarn off to the side and I couldnt kill the damn things fast enough. Only got CS to myself for about an hour though before a wizard came in a ruined my whole plan. /bonk wizzy_468.<br>
<br>
BTW, my earth pet focused or not can solo any damn Wyvern in CS cept Volcarn (twit) and those dern drakes... i use air pet against drakes... they cant land there w33k little AoE on Jabober when he's in tornado form.<br>
<br>
l8rz all.<br>
